description:
Add all new CSS rules to src/ui/static/styles.css. Rules needed:
- a.stat-card { cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; color: inherit; transition: border-color 0.15s ease }
- a.stat-card:hover { border-color: var(--color-accent) }
- .quick-section (compact 5-row preview block for front page)
- .quick-section__header (flex row: h2 + right-aligned 'View all →' link)
- .pagination (flex row, gap, centered)
- .pagination a { border: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; border-radius: var(--radius) }
- .pagination .current { color: var(--color-accent); border-color: var(--color-accent) }
No new design tokens. All new pages depend on these classes existing.
